{"tid":658356,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[共諜坐監終老]居港CIA特工被控非法保留機密資料 最高可囚終身","createTime":"2018-05-09T01:58:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T16:40:53.000Z","uid":132859,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f12182dd5470f8770e96336b4fb9570ce685ec55","tid":658356,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T01:58:17.000Z","msg":"居港的美國中央情報局（CIA）前主任李振成（Jerry Chun Shing Lee　音），被美國控以蒐集機密資料，企圖交予中國政府，若罪成最高面臨終身監禁。<br />\n<br />\n美國司法部周二表示，53歲的李振成被維珍尼亞州聯邦大陪審團，控以一項串謀蒐集或發放國防資料以協助外國政府，以及兩項非法保留涉及國防的文件罪。<br />\n<br />\n李振成1月在香港飛抵紐約甘迺迪機場時被捕。法庭文件顯示他在夏威夷取得碩士學位後，1994年加入CIA，至2007年離職，不過他仍保留高度機密資料。傳媒指他幫中國做間諜，將駐華線人絕密資料交給中方，令至少12名在華的線人被殺或被囚，美國對華情報工作處於癱瘓，成為美國近30年來最大的情報災難。<br />\n<br />\n司法部文件顯示，兩名中國情報人員2010年接觸李振成，向他「買料」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180509/58169467\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180509%2F58169467&d=VxHlKThWSdpvBcndEwljImxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=f853b0f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180509%2F58169467&h=7d22086c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180509/58169467</a><br />\n祝你* --&gt; O<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"049ebb33b997fac6f28008627623de87f0a544a9","tid":658356,"uid":84081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T02:02:57.000Z","msg":"Pick up da soap .jpg"},{"pid":"60019695ab66d68eeaa3d8747065a55e9064f55b","tid":658356,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T02:17:13.000Z","msg":"唔知會唔會同肥何一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568cb158b92321c6294b6890fd837